Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回去路上当心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  小博  今天要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尝些甜点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是进行八朔节的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这几个选项吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花  别太粘着九澄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁喉技  锁喉技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  某个电视剧里说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱越是坎坷就越激烈来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能输  来场激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  还打算一起回去的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来今天小要当班呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  作为图书委员工作比较忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是自己想要调查一些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个看起来挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学  还是先把这些放到桌上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好跟上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想调查的是嫦娥镇流传的民间传说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是都市传说那样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市传说是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说就是现代版的怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排成队伍的红色萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜  在旧市街的小路上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人目击到发着红光的萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说看到的人就会遇上不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可思议的是  这种萤火虫却没有被实际发现过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫦娥镇流行种植八朔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔有八分切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说有撕得粉碎的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以八朔也是猎奇杀人的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  挺有趣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…就这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有点暧昧的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能有那种搞笑点的结局就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是相声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市传说吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  小要对那些还真是着迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好将来拜小博父亲为师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不会了  以她的热情程度完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  星期一要好好做八朔节的练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要做那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  八朔节马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  小博  下周见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的没那种兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你聊聊  学校的事什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太大声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  学校的事的话就叫上小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃会碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一诚前辈  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一小时  三十分钟也行  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他只是有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是太热了所以头有点昏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来就不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去倒些水来  稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了  真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  麻奈  你在生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说散步一个人也能行而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛  老爸说让我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明平时都不听话的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  难得一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好好享受景色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼…的雕像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼…和老爸说的嫦娥狼的传说有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了就告诉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一定会咬住不放的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  那目光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在注视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说是不是发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪是没事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明突然就开始走神了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小提琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让心情平静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是白狼大人的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  真是很棒的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  不介意的话喝点茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请务必让我们品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请  不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你叫麻奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的姓一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫真那香织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}注：真那也读mana
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果麻奈是我们家的孩子  就该叫真那麻奈了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位哥哥也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:11:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能合你口味太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得不好意思  突然就受到这样的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意  我平时都在招待邻居和路过的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一个人生活  所以想要有人陪我说话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  香织姐姐  你平时都在拉小提琴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有时间的时候就拉  虽然技术不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我说不好  但我很感动的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈喜欢小提琴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然没有拉过  不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总觉得  这音色真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拉拉看？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我不是太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:13:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个  我想会顺手的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我像麻奈你这么大的时候用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就从姿势开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀放松
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用左肩和下巴下面支撑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当的有模有样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  哥哥你可不要随便乱说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就实际拉拉看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先从基本的基本开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  香织老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然叫我老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  老哥  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥的话出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是去「中心」拿胶囊去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不用担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你哥哥和你都是我家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  中心的储备已经很少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次能给你的量  这就是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  休息日叫你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因为我也有事要出来办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那个  我一直在犹豫要不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢…前辈你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第一次见面时就喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道前辈你很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好几次我都想放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  可不可以请你下车？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定会回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在  你下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  打搅你这么长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么打搅  我很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈  下次再练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次你一定能拉出更美的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个漂亮的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉非常的高雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓音如其人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你又说那种自以为很了解的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种温柔的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有香织小姐才拉得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不  只是有点迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  可以的话我来为您指路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三重子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  帽子忘记在香织姐姐那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我现在马上就去拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  已经不早了  明天再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  好啦  毕竟香织小姐也会在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来您是在做地质学的调查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您拿着地图  我还以为您是来观光的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我经常被人误会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是研究生院的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合您的口味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  这红茶很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是茶叶  泡的方式也很用心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在说这种无聊话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君  怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  妹妹把帽子给忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  研究期间有空请再过来坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会的话就来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织小姐的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是今天才遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我到底做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动静好像就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情我全都知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的…萤火虫！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱他  他也爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明  只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢上他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是不会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不可能会明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上别人这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么而生下来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  回答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了…维护戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  警察先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  来人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么打不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人  来人  来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说谎  请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的  的确是在这里  一个女人拿着巨大的镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇里  有着充满了谜团的杀人集团
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:17.99,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:17.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:28.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが信じた愛の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:28.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信之情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:34.95,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱きしめた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:34.95,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:37.81,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影が月でなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:37.81,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影非月  月非影
